<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8"?><song><author>Nur Shoh</author>
<lyrics>[C1]
   Endi kuylar dilim shoʻx bulbullarday
   Yuragim hapriqar sevgan dillarday
   Dunyoni tashvishi xalal bermaydi
   Yasharman huzuringda farishtalarday.

[V1]
 Dilim torlarini chertganda doim
 Nolayu figʻonlar hasrat qilardi
 Sen keldingu qalbimga bugun ey Rabbim
 Kuylarimni jarangi butkul oʻzgardi.

[C2]
   Endi kuylar dilim shoʻx bulbullarday
   Yuragim hapriqar sevgan dillarday
   Dunyoni tashvishi xalal bermaydi
   Yasharman huzuringda farishtalarday.

[V2]
 Qadaming qutlugʻdir farzandlaringga
 Sevgingdan mehringdan toʻymayman sira
 Qudrating oldida egarman boshim
 Sen aziz muhtaram eng oliy Rabbim.

[C3]
   Endi kuylar dilim shoʻx bulbullarday
   Yuragim hapriqar sevgan dillarday
   Dunyoni tashvishi xalal bermaydi
   Yasharman huzuringda farishtalarday.</lyrics>
<title>Endi kuylar dilim</title>
</song>